00:35:15,716 --> 00:35:16,925
Monsieur Chocolat!

457
00:35:17,133 --> 00:35:17,966
Vous êtes là.

458
00:35:18,175 --> 00:35:19,758
Si, si, y a quelqu'un.

459
00:35:19,925 --> 00:35:20,841
Si. Si.

460
00:35:21,008 --> 00:35:22,175
Je le sais bien.

461
00:35:22,425 --> 00:35:24,050
Atchiktchiboum!

462
00:35:30,508 --> 00:35:32,800
- À vos souhaits.
- Merci.

463
00:35:49,758 --> 00:35:50,883
il est passé où?

464
00:35:53,633 --> 00:35:54,925
- Footit!
- Ah!

465
00:36:04,383 --> 00:36:05,550
Footit!

466
00:36:09,175 --> 00:36:10,883
- Footit!
- J'ai eu peur.

467
00:36:11,091 --> 00:36:12,175
Ah oui?

468
00:36:16,966 --> 00:36:18,883
Atchiktchiboum!

469
00:36:41,758 --> 00:36:42,675
Atchi...

470
00:37:06,133 --> 00:37:07,591
Non. Non.

471
00:37:25,425 --> 00:37:26,675
Footit!

472
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:38,683
Non.

473
00:37:42,550 --> 00:37:44,508
- Après vous.
- Avec plaisir.

474
00:37:44,716 --> 00:37:46,258
- Restez poli.
- Bien à vous.

475
00:37:46,508 --> 00:37:47,358
Cordialement.

476
00:37:47,508 --> 00:37:48,716
- Condoléances.
- Absolument.

477
00:37:48,883 --> 00:37:50,175
S'il vous plaît!

478
00:38:07,758 --> 00:38:08,925
Chocolat!

479
00:38:09,133 --> 00:38:10,008
Vous êtes beau.

480
00:38:10,966 --> 00:38:11,883
Ah oui?

481
00:38:12,091 --> 00:38:13,258
- Je vous dessine.
- Merci.

482
00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:20,425
M. Footit!
Je vais tomber!

483
00:38:20,633 --> 00:38:21,841
Attendez.

484
00:38:22,050 --> 00:38:24,466
Ah! Je vais tomber!

485
00:38:26,758 --> 00:38:27,800
Regardez pas en bas!

486
00:38:27,966 --> 00:38:29,216
C'est trop tard!

487
00:38:45,675 --> 00:38:46,675
Plus bouger.

488
00:38:46,883 --> 00:38:48,008
- Vous bougez.
- Non.

489
00:38:48,216 --> 00:38:50,550
Si!
Ne bougez plus!

490
00:38:54,133 --> 00:38:55,925
Regardez, alors là, c'est...

491
00:38:56,133 --> 00:38:56,966
C'est...

492
00:38:57,175 --> 00:38:58,050
Hein?

493
00:39:03,216 --> 00:39:04,175
Là!

494
00:39:04,425 --> 00:39:05,633
